### Use REST Client
### Create a new artwork
POST http://localhost:8080/artworks
content-type: application/json

{
    "title": "Sunset over the hills",
    "file_path": "storage/artworks/sunset_123.jpg",
    "source_url": "https://artstation.com/artwork/sunset-hills",
    "p_hash": "bf62c82e1a3f4b5d",
    "meta_data": {},
    "artist_id": 1
}

### Find artwork by perceptual hash
GET http://localhost:8080/artworks/hash/bf62c82e1a3f4b5d

### List all artworks by a specific artist
GET http://localhost:8080/artists/1/artworks

### Update artwork metadata
PATCH http://localhost:8080/artworks/1/metadata
content-type: application/json

{
    "meta_data": {"tags": ["landscape", "nature", "sunset"]}
}